Preheat oven to 375 degrees F. In medium bowl, combine graham cracker crumbs, flour and baking powder; set aside. Beat EAGLE BRAND(r) and butter until smooth; add reserved crumb mixture, mixing well. Stir in coconut, chocolate pieces and holiday bits. Drop by rounded teaspoonfuls onto greased cookie sheets. Bake 7 to 9 minutes or until lightly browned. Cool 1 minute; transfer from cookie sheet to wire rack. Cool completely. Store leftovers tightly covered at room temperature.